title: Husky Liners “Great Workout”  - Cargo Liners Product Features
description: Meet Drew Force. He is an aspiring (or struggling) surfer. Nonetheless, he puts the Husky Liners Cargo Liner to the test. Our Cargo Liners protect and defend your trunk and cargo areas from whatever you throw at them. These liners are custom fit with high perimeter edges and an anti-slip surface, minimizing slipping and sliding as well as protecting your ride from inevitable spills and mess.
tags: Husky Liners, Cargo Liners, Cargo Mat, Trunk Liner
